Subject: [PATCH] Implement --with-target-bindir

This option was present in configure since 4.08.0, but not actually
implemented.

(cherry picked from commit c54f87a82174c779aa9ea54b9317b544459bd19b)
(cherry picked from commit 764a319677b982df3b8d54349f88550b99b80683)

